&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;**THIS VACANCY IS ONLY OPEN TO EMPLOYEES OF WORCESTERSHIRE ACUTE HOSPITALS NHS TRUST**&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Endoscopy Booking Team is looking to recruit Endoscopy Booking Co-ordinators to support the Countywide Endoscopy Service. We are looking for enthusiastic individuals to join our friendly teams.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The job role is varied and will require the individual to be able to adapt well, manage all duties effectively and be able to work in a fast paced environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will need to be reliable, flexible, and hard working. Excellent communication skills and IT skills are a must. Delivery of deadlines is key to this role; you will be expected to work with the team and also as individuals using initiative.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;There is a requirement to travel between Worcestershire Royal Hospital,Kidderminster Hospital &amp; Treatment Centre,Alexandra Hospital and Evesham Community Hospital.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;For further details, please contact Sarah Bailey on 01905 763333 ext. 30280 or Louise Burgess on 01562 826328 or ext. 53359&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
